{"metadata":{"name":"Sunan Ibn Majah","section":{"9":"The Chapters on Marriage"},"section_detail":{"9":{"hadithnumber_first":1845,"hadithnumber_last":2015,"arabicnumber_first":1845,"arabicnumber_last":2015}}},"hadiths":[{"hadithnumber":1952,"arabicnumber":1952,"text":"Rapporté par Qais bin Harith : « Je me suis converti à l’islam et j’avais huit femmes. Je suis allé voir le Prophète et je lui ai parlé de cela. Il a dit : “Choisis-en quatre.” »","grades":[{"name":"Al-Albani","grade":"Hasan Sahih"},{"name":"Muhammad Fouad Abd al-Baqi","grade":"Hasan Sahih"},{"name":"Shuaib Al Arnaut","grade":"Daif"},{"name":"Zubair Ali Zai","grade":"Daif"}],"reference":{"book":9,"hadith":108}}]}